PX3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, 'union' is just another word for Mafia.
~z~It's my duty to watch this cat's back.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~替这伙计两肋插刀是我的责任。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~The union won't bend over because of you.
~z~What are you suggesting we do about it?
~z~Well, I need money. This pays. I can do it...
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我缺钱，你这活给钱。我能搞定...

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I guess you can see that the guy got away.
~z~We're gonna fight to keep these jobs in American hands.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我们要为美国人的岗位抗争到底。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~This is a union matter. Get fucked.
~z~Show them punkass bitches they be fucking with a businessman.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~让他们那群小贱人知道他们惹的是商人。(BETA)

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You gonna go in there and get them Mafia types off the site.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~你冲进去，把那群黑手党从工地上赶走。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~If it's a union problem, doesn't that make it bigger than a few guys with guns?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~既然是工会问题，光把武装分子干掉也没用吧？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Ladies, gimme a few minutes. Business calls.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~女士们，等我几分钟。工作优先。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~My ancestors came from Africa, now he's coming out a bit later.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我祖上是非洲来的，他不过是来晚了点。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~That all them lookouts gone, money. Get in there and free up the site.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~放哨的都挂了，老弟。进去解放工地吧。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~If I get rid of the guys on the site, then won't there be more?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~要是我除掉了工地上的人，不是会有更多人来吗？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~There's also a radio headset in there, so me and you can keep in communication.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~里面还有套头戴式对讲机，这样我们就能保持联络了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I think you might want to look at a map, Playboy. Dubai isn't in Africa.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我觉得你该去看下地图，Playboy。迪拜不在非洲。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Hell, this Slavic motherfucker any good, he could help you.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~你看，这个斯拉夫混蛋也很能干，他能帮上你。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Well I'm always looking for good guys. Build an army.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我一直在招贤纳士。搞一个军团。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~This ain't none of your business, shitbird.
~z~No man. I'd just confuse shit if I went in with you.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~不来，老弟。我跟你一起上只会弄得更加难办。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Some Italian dudes has shut down his building site on some union bullshit.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~一些意大利人靠什么工会让他的工地停工了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, you a cold motherfucker. Next guy is south of your position, up a few stories in the next building.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~操，你这冷酷的混蛋。下一个人在你的南边，隔壁那栋楼再上去几层。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I knew you was the right Slavic killer for this job.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我就知道你是我要找的斯拉夫杀手。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~But in my work... people change. Money changes people.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~不过替我干活的...都变了个人。金钱会改变人。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You just take that shit in your stride.
~z~See you soon, Playboy. I'll try to save a grenade so you can have fun with one, too.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~回头见，Playboy。我会尽量留一颗手雷给你玩玩的。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I saw you handle yourself for Elizabeta the other day.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~之前我在Elizabeta那儿见识过你的能耐了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~They all up in the place, strapped to their fronts with hardhats on and shit. Won't let nobody get near it.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~他们占领了工地，戴着安全帽拿武器守在那边。谁都不让靠近。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~There's a cat in the south west corner of the yard by the water. Get him.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~工地西南角的海旁边还有个人，做掉他。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Man, I would have laid on a party, got some freaks out... shit...
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~哥，早知道我就叫几个伙计来开派对了...去...

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Yo, money. There's a chopper turning up.
~z~Man, there better be a good view from the top.
~z~Later on. If you can't see anything else from up here, you'll see these grenades going off.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~等着吧，就算上面视野不好，手榴弹爆炸你总看得见。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I'm gonna get into position where I can see all the shit going down.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我就到能看见下面情况的制高点上去。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Do I look like I live low budget, dog?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我看着像是过便宜日子的人吗，老弟？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You goin' to go in there and clear out those motherfuckers.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~你就进去，然后把那群狗日的都给干咯。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Niko - Dwayne Forge. He taught me everything I know.
~z~What you doing? Get that motherfucker, motherfucker.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~你在干什么？狗日的快干掉那个狗日的。(BETA)

PX3AUD.original: ~z~If the union says this site is shut, it's shut. Capiche?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~工会说停工，那就得停工。明白吗？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~This guy's a big developer? Are you and him having meetings about how to run the city?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~这人是个大开发商？你是不是要和他去开会讨论怎么管理城市？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Oh, hey, now I ain't saying that.
~z~and I heard good things about you.
~z~That's if you're hoping to talk a bunch of Mafia owned union officials off of a building site they've shut down.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~不然你咋跟那个黑手党手下的工会谈判，让他们离开被迫停工的工地呢。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I wouldn't want you after my ass.
~z~A badass ma'fucker who ain't afraid to take fools down.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~一个不介意做掉几个蠢蛋的大恶人。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Not exactly going to be turning them heads, is it?
~z~As you can see, this place is going to need a cleanup before any workers come in.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~如你所见，在有工人进来前，最好先把这地方清扫一下。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You gonna kick some ass down there, boy. I'm backing you up.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~待会你下去干烂他们，小子。我在后方支援你。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~That all them lookouts gone, money. Get in there and free up the site.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~放哨的都挂了，老弟。进去解放工地吧。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You getting that mad money on this one.
~z~Not yet, but I got an idea about how me and him can get friendly.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~还没，不过我已经想到该怎么和他搞好关系了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~What you mean, what's the plan? Pick up where we left off.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~「有打算吗」是几个意思？重拾旧业啊。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I don't care if I live or die...
~z~Yo, there's three lookout cats making sure no one makes move on the site.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~看，那边有三个放哨的伙计，负责保证没人靠近工地。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I don't gotta be the persuasive one, money. You do.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~用不着我去说服他们，老弟。你去。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You know Yusuf Amir, the big real estate developer?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~听说过Yusuf Amir吗，那个房产大开发商？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You the right man for this job, money.
~z~I got rid of all the union problems on this site.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~工地的工会问题我都解决了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Alright, you heard a Yusuf Amir? Big real estate developer.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，你听说过Yusuf Amir吗？房产大开发商。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, well I need money so you're in luck.
~z~That cat and me is going to be tight as two cellmates on lockdown after this.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~之后那伙计跟我就会铁得跟蹲过一个牢房一样。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~What you doin', motherfucker? We need us a ride.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~狗日的你在干嘛？我们得找辆车。(BETA)

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I'm givin' you them dollar bills, and when Playboy pays, he pays big!
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我会给你一堆钞票，一旦Playboy付钱，那就是一大笔钱！

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Make the Mafia cats go away so the workers can come in and everything will be cool.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~赶跑那群黑手党，工人就能进来了，然后什么都好说。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~But when they hear about this shit they gonna start listening to Playboy.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~不过只要听说了这回事，他们就会听我Playboy说话了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I don't know. I've heard a lot of names since I got here.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~没听说过，我到这儿以后已经听说了一大堆名字了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~If you can take out the main cats then the rest of them shouldn't be a problem.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~只要把几个头头解决了，剩下的就不成问题。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Well, I heard on the grapevine that he's run into a heap of trouble with some union cats.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我听说他惹上了一群工会的家伙。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~The last guy is to your east. Shit, money. You best watch yourself. There be more of these Mafia cats turning up.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~最后一个在你的东边。操，老弟。自己当心点。那边的黑手党伙计更多。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~What the fuck's he tryin' to prove?
~z~Shit, you doing this for a paycheck.
~z~Now you know I'll do anything I can.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~这你总知道我会尽己所能了吧。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You're going to have to be a pretty persuasive guy.
~z~I'm going to call Mr. Yusuf Amir, tell him the good news.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我这就打给Yusuf Amir先生，跟他报个喜。(BETA)

PX3AUD.original: ~z~This shit is Mafia run and they all over his construction site with guns and shit.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~说白了是黑手党干的，他们全副武装地守着工地。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You ain't bringing in no immigrant scabs. We're gonna fight to keep this place closed.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~别想让移民进来工作，我们要靠斗争让这里长期停工。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~We going to Castle Gardens. There's an alley we want to hit up just off the South Parkway.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我们去Castle Gardens。South Parkway那边有条小巷，我们就去那。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Damn, money. I thought you was gonna do this shit for sure.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~干，老弟。我还以为这点屁事你肯定能成。(BETA)

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Hmmm... okay... oh, I just want to get in there and make shit happen.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~唔...行吧...哦，我只是想进去搞点事情。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, I needed to find a cat like you.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~靠，我要的就是你这样的伙计。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I'm out. I'm back. We keep on rollin'.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我出来了，回归了。咱们接着干啊。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You best take them out with the rifle before you hit up the rest of them.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~你进去之前最好先用狙把他们解决了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~They stopping Amir from sending in the scabs.
~z~Yo, can you hear me, player? This thing best be working for your sake.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~哟，听得见吗，玩家？这东西最好是能用。(BETA)

PX3AUD.original: ~z~What? Your silk sheet, fancy dress wearing life too big for me now?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~咋了？你锦衣玉食的日子我就不配过了？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Amongst other things. I don't know how good your plan is though, Playboy.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~算最需要的吧。不过我不确定你这计划能否实现，Playboy。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You the money, son. Yusuf's PA won't put me through to the cat.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~好本事，小子。Yusuf的秘书不帮我转接给他。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I'll tell you where the cats are at and who you need to look out for. I'm your eyes in the sky, money.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我会告诉你人都在哪儿，要找的是谁。我就是你的天眼，老弟。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I think our boy is making a run for it. Get him good.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我觉得那小子要乘着它跑了，快做掉他。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~When you in there, I'll give you the lowdown on where these main cats is at.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~等你进去了，我会跟你讲几个头头在哪里。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Not me. I'm still a hustler from these streets...
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我没变。我还是那个街头出身的欺诈师...

PX3AUD.original: ~z~So, these things don't half go slowly, eh?
~z~These cats is looking to squeeze our boy Amir for dollars just because he ain't from here.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~这些伙计因为我们的Amir兄弟不是本地人就想敲诈他一笔。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~So hey, man. Where you staying? D'you need some money? What's the plan?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~那，嘿，哥。现在住哪儿？缺钱吗？有打算吗？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Keep an eye on that wannabe asshole...
~z~I'll give you what you after. Cold hard cash. That what you chasing, right?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~你要什么我给什么。真金白银，这就是你要的吧？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~He's an African, an he's comin' to Liberty City to make it big.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~他是非洲人，他来自由城就是为了把事业做大。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~This sounds like a pretty bad deal for me, don't it, Playboy?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~那我好像很划不来啊，是不是，Playboy？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Yeah. You could say that. So, why do you need me?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~对，可以这么说吧。那你又为什么需要我？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~All them tiny ants down there. Man, shit is crazy.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~下面一群蝼蚁。老弟，太他妈疯狂了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You ain't gonna be able to beat the union.
~z~Shit, I can feel the heat from up here.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~操，我在上面都能感受到热浪了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Alright, can you make this thing go any quicker?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我说，这玩意就不能速度快点吗？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Because I'm a clever motherfucker. I'm using my God-given intellect.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~因为我太他妈聪明了。我用上了我天生的才智。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~When we fuck their people up they'll realize that he ain't a cat to be messed with and they'll back off.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~等我们把他们的手下干烂，他们就会知道Amir不是他们能惹的人，然后收手。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~This is my ticket to the big time, baby. I'm about to make it, for real.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~这是我成为大人物的敲门砖。我就要成功了，真的。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I left some heat for you in that car, money. You going to be strapped - sniper rifles, grenades, all that shit.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我在那辆车里给你准备了些家伙，老弟。会给你武装上的——狙击枪，手榴弹，各种各样。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Alright, you in, money? The first guy is on the scaffolding in the building to the east of the yard.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~好了，你进去了没，老弟？第一个人在工地东面的脚手架上。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~The people who helped me get to the top.
~z~Yusuf is in some problems. Playboy is going to come in there and help him out.
~z~Boom! You mean business, don't you, boy?
~z~This is getting awkward. Talk about a slow lift.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~说到很慢的电梯，这就很怪了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~There's all types a' scaffolding and shit in the construction yard.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~工地里边杂七杂八的脚手架啥的太多了。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You might be better seeing the lookouts from up here too, money.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~你最好也上来，上面可以看见那些放哨的，老弟。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~What about that guy, Dwayne? You going to forget about him?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~那Dwayne呢，他又怎样？你是要忘记他吗？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~You didn't tell me you was getting out!
~z~Me and him could be cousins, shit.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我跟他说不定还是远房亲戚来的，天。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~There's someone here for you. Dwayne or some shit. I don't know.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~有人找你，好像是Dwayne还是啥的。我不清楚。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Meantime, I'm gonna tell Yusuf how good we been to him.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~然后，我就跟Yusuf去讲我们帮了他多大的忙。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, it all the same. Africa, America, Dubai.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~管他，都一样的。非洲，美洲，迪拜。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Stupid immigrants. Trying to take American jobs.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~蠢蛋移民。还想抢美国人的工作。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~That cat going to be back. Hit me up later.
~z~I'm gonna get into a position where I can see everything goin' down.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我就到能看见下面情况的制高点上去。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Don't go fucking up this site too bad, you hear?
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~别把工地搞得太乱，听见了没？

PX3AUD.original: ~z~It don't matter, we're brothers, spiritually I mean, and that's the important bit.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~无所谓，反正我们是兄弟，精神上的兄弟，这才是关键。

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Yo, you definitely is from Eastern Europe. Driving this shit.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~哟，开这么辆破车，你肯定是东欧来的。(BETA)

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Looks like that's the last of them. Now you just need to get the hell out of there, money.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~看来那些就是最后一波了。现在你只要逃出来就行了，老弟。(BETA)

PX3AUD.original: ~z~I left some heat for you in that car, money. Pop the trunk and take what you need.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~我在那辆车里给你准备了些家伙，老弟。自己上车拿吧。(BETA)

PX3AUD.original: ~z~Don't worry, money. When I'm big time, I won't forget about cats like you.
PX3AUD.translated: ~z~别担心，老弟。等我成了大人物，也不会忘记你这个小弟的。
